{"text_id":229340,"tokens":["The"," use"," of"," facial"," recognition"," technology"," in"," education"," has"," been"," a"," hot"," button"," issue"," for"," some"," time"," now","."," On"," one"," side",","," some"," argue"," that"," utilizing"," this"," type"," of"," technology"," can"," improve"," security",","," reduce"," costs",","," and"," provide"," valuable"," data"," to"," schools"," and"," teachers","."," On"," the"," other"," side",","," however",","," many"," people"," are"," concerned"," about"," the"," privacy"," implications"," of"," this"," technology"," as"," well"," as"," the"," overall"," reduction"," in"," the"," role"," of"," human"," teachers"," as"," technology"," becomes"," more"," prominent",".","\n\n","In"," terms"," of"," security",","," facial"," recognition"," technology"," can"," help"," keep"," students"," and"," faculty"," safe"," by"," verifying"," the"," identity"," of"," those"," entering"," the"," school","."," This"," technology"," can"," be"," used"," to"," quickly"," and"," accurately"," identify"," individuals"," and"," prevent"," the"," entry"," of"," dangerous"," individuals"," into"," the"," building","."," Additionally",","," utilizing"," facial"," recognition"," technology"," can"," also"," help"," reduce"," costs"," associated"," with"," man","ning"," the"," entrance"," to"," the"," school","."," In"," terms"," of"," data"," collection",","," facial"," recognition"," technology"," can"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," classroom"," and"," student"," performance",".","\n\n","Despite"," the"," potential"," benefits"," of"," facial"," recognition"," technology",","," there"," are"," also"," concerns"," surrounding"," privacy"," and"," the"," reduction"," in"," the"," role"," of"," human"," teachers","."," In"," terms"," of"," privacy",","," there"," is"," concern"," that"," facial"," recognition"," technology"," could"," be"," used"," for"," surveillance"," purposes",","," something"," that"," could"," ultimately"," impinge"," on"," the"," rights"," of"," students"," and"," faculty","."," Additionally",","," there"," is"," a"," concern"," that"," as"," technology"," advances",","," human"," teachers"," could"," be"," increasingly"," replaced"," by"," machines",","," resulting"," in"," a"," less"," exciting"," learning"," environment",".","\n\n","Overall",","," facial"," recognition"," technology"," does"," have"," potential"," value"," in"," education","."," However",","," it"," should"," be"," used"," cautiously"," and"," with"," a"," full"," understanding"," of"," the"," potential"," privacy"," implications","."," Additionally",","," while"," technology"," does"," have"," its"," place",","," it"," should"," not"," be"," used"," as"," a"," replacement"," for"," the"," important"," role"," of"," human"," teachers",","," who"," bring"," a"," sense"," of"," humanity"," and"," joy"," to"," the"," learning"," experience","."," Ultimately",","," facial"," recognition"," technology"," in"," education"," can"," have"," value"," if"," it"," is"," used"," properly"," and"," serves"," to"," enhance",","," rather"," than"," replace",","," the"," human"," element"," of"," teaching","."," ","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," facial"," recognition"," technology"," has"," some"," valuable"," applications"," in"," the"," world"," of"," education",","," it"," should"," be"," tempered"," with"," a"," focus"," on"," privacy"," and"," the"," role"," of"," human"," teachers","."," Used"," properly",","," facial"," recognition"," technology"," can"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," and"," improve"," safety",","," without"," sacrificing"," privacy"," or"," human"," teachers","."," ","\n\n","The"," value"," of"," facial"," recognition"," technology"," in"," education"," and"," the"," role"," of"," human"," teachers"," are"," two"," intertwined"," concepts","."," Used"," properly",","," facial"," recognition"," technology"," can"," provide"," some"," valuable"," insights"," and","